inline Elements ==> input , label , textarea
block element ==> form

form attributes ==> autocomplete(off , on)
input & textarea attributes ==> name , readonly ,  disabled , placeholder , value , maxlength , minlength
input attribute ==> type (text , email , password , number , radio , date , datetime-local , month , range , color , file ) , autocomplete
textarea attribute => rows , cols
input type radio/checkbox ==> checked
input type range ==> max , min , step 
input type file / select ==> multiple
option ==> selected